## Description {#details}

A data type for representing the result computed by <code>computeDependence</code>.

States whether it is okay to reorder the instruction passed to <code>computeDependence</code> with at most one dependency.

Definition at line 92 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/implicitnullchecks-cpp">ImplicitNullChecks.cpp</a>.
